<content type="html" xml:base="http://www.classicshell.net/forum/viewtopic.php?t=4784&amp;p=21330#p21330"><![CDATA[
Blue single it is. I'm skipping caption as it looked bad. <br />I'll make an option for two column to have all blue, or split.<br />Starting to make some headway. At the beginning, I converted too much at once, <br />without checking the progress. Bad move, as all I got was the default no skin white menu, <br />without any skin error notification. Probably cause I had so many. <img src="http://www.classicshell.net/forum/images/smilies/icon_lol.gif" alt=":lol:" title="Laughing" /> <br />Has this ever happened to you? <br />This is now the third time, starting from scratch, <br />and I'm making backup copies every once in a while, just to be safe.<br /><br />100% is one of the hardest, as the button is so big.<br />I have to devise sneaky compromise ways of shrinking it, making it line up.<br />You will still have to either delete the separator above power button, <br />or add a blank custom item in CSM customize tab, to make it look better.<br />Tuesday now. Will probably finish it by Friday, no promises.<br />Time to sleep.<br /><br />Cheerio<p>Statistics: Posted by <a href="http://www.classicshell.net/forum/memberlist.php?mode=viewprofile&amp;u=856">juniper7</a> — Tue Aug 18, 2015 1:47 am</p><hr />
